<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>

<title>Purnisha — Prompt Engineering Guide</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
}

:root{
    --bg:#efefef;
    --card:#ffffff;
    --dark:#0f0f10;
    --text:#2f2f33;
    --muted:#757575;
    --border:#e8e8e8;
    --shadow:0 15px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
}

body{
    background:linear-gradient(to bottom right,#f3f3f3,#ebebeb);
    font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
    color:var(--text);
    overflow-x:hidden;
}

body::before{
    content:'';
    position:fixed;
    top:0;
    right:0;
    width:400px;
    height:400px;
    background-image:radial-gradient(#d8d8d8 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size:14px 14px;
    opacity:0.5;
    z-index:-1;
}

.container{
    width:100%;
    max-width:1400px;
    margin:auto;
    padding:60px 40px;
}

.grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(320px,1fr));
    gap:40px;
    align-items:start;
}

.card{
    background:var(--card);
    border-radius:38px;
    overflow:hidden;
    box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    position:relative;
    transition:0.4s ease;
}

.card:hover{
    transform:translateY(-8px);
}

.dark-card{
    background:#101012;
    color:white;
}

.dark-card p{
    color:#bdbdbd;
}

.hero{
    padding:45px;
}

.small-tag{
    font-size:12px;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    letter-spacing:2px;
    color:#9d9d9d;
    margin-bottom:25px;
    font-weight:600;
}

.title{
    font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
    font-size:48px;
    line-height:1;
    margin-bottom:20px;
}

.subtitle{
    font-size:16px;
    color:var(--muted);
    line-height:1.8;
}

.profile{
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:space-between;
    margin-bottom:35px;
}

.profile img{
    width:72px;
    height:72px;
    border-radius:50%;
    object-fit:cover;
}

.button-row{
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:center;
    margin-top:40px;
}

.btn{
    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    padding:18px 30px;
    border-radius:18px;
    background:transparent;
    color:white;
    font-size:14px;
    letter-spacing:0.5px;
}

.price{
    font-size:38px;
    font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
}

.image-section img{
    width:100%;
    height:450px;
    object-fit:cover;
    display:block;
}

.content{
    padding:40px;
}

.content h2{
    font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
    font-size:38px;
    margin-bottom:18px;
    line-height:1.1;
}

.content p{
    color:var(--muted);
    line-height:1.9;
    margin-bottom:20px;
}

.info-box{
    background:#f7f7f7;
    border-radius:24px;
    padding:25px;
    margin-top:30px;
}

.info-box h4{
    font-size:13px;
    letter-spacing:1px;
    margin-bottom:10px;
}

.info-box p{
    font-size:14px;
    margin-bottom:12px;
}

.two-column{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
    gap:20px;
}

.mini-card{
    background:white;
    border-radius:22px;
    padding:20px;
    border:1px solid var(--border);
}

.mini-card img{
    width:100%;
    height:180px;
    object-fit:cover;
    border-radius:18px;
    margin-bottom:15px;
}

.mini-title{
    font-size:15px;
    font-weight:600;
    margin-bottom:8px;
}

.mini-sub{
    font-size:13px;
    color:var(--muted);
}

.quote{
    padding:45px;
    background:white;
}

.quote-text{
    font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
    font-size:38px;
    line-height:1.3;
    margin-bottom:25px;
}

.line{
    width:80px;
    height:1px;
    background:#d5d5d5;
    margin:25px 0;
}

.stats{
    display:flex;
    gap:40px;
    margin-top:30px;
}

.stat h3{
    font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
    font-size:40px;
}

.stat p{
    font-size:12px;
    letter-spacing:1px;
    color:var(--muted);
    text-transform:uppercase;
}

.footer{
    text-align:center;
    margin-top:70px;
    color:#8b8b8b;
    font-size:14px;
    letter-spacing:1px;
}

@media(max-width:900px){

    .container{
        padding:30px 20px;
    }

    .title{
        font-size:40px;
    }

    .content h2{
        font-size:32px;
    }

    .quote-text{
        font-size:30px;
    }

}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

    <div class="grid">

        <!-- CARD 1 -->

        <div class="card dark-card hero">

            <div class="profile">

                <div>
                    <div class="small-tag">Prompt Engineering</div>

                    <h1 class="title">
                        Think Like <br>
                        A Strategist
                    </h1>
                </div>

                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544005313-94ddf0286df2?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="">
            </div>

            <p class="subtitle">
                Prompting is not about asking better questions.
                It is about designing cognition, perspective,
                structure, and intelligence.
            </p>

            <div class="button-row">

                <button class="btn">
                    Explore Guide
                </button>

                <div class="price">
                    AI
                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

        <!-- CARD 2 -->

        <div class="card">

            <div class="image-section">

                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518998053901-5348d3961a04?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="">

            </div>

            <div class="content">

                <div class="small-tag">
                    Cognitive Architecture
                </div>

                <h2>
                    The 6-Layer Prompt Formula
                </h2>

                <p>
                    Identity. Context. Outcome. Constraints.
                    Structure. Iteration.
                </p>

                <p>
                    Elite prompting is the ability to shape
                    intelligence outputs with precision and elegance.
                </p>

                <div class="info-box">

                    <h4>
                        HIGH LEVEL THINKING
                    </h4>

                    <p>
                        The quality of your prompts directly affects
                        the sophistication of your thinking.
                    </p>

                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

        <!-- CARD 3 -->

        <div class="card quote">

            <div class="small-tag">
                Core Philosophy
            </div>

            <div class="quote-text">
                “Strong prompts create strategic intelligence.”
            </div>

            <div class="line"></div>

            <p class="subtitle">
                Most people use AI for convenience.
                Strategic people use AI for cognitive augmentation.
            </p>

            <div class="stats">

                <div class="stat">
                    <h3>6</h3>
                    <p>Layers</p>
                </div>

                <div class="stat">
                    <h3>∞</h3>
                    <p>Possibilities</p>
                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

        <!-- CARD 4 -->

        <div class="card">

            <div class="image-section">

                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516321497487-e288fb19713f?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="">

            </div>

            <div class="content">

                <div class="small-tag">
                    Advanced Methods
                </div>

                <h2>
                    Multi-Expert Prompting
                </h2>

                <p>
                    Analyze situations from the perspective of:
                    strategists, psychologists, founders,
                    economists, and communication experts.
                </p>

                <div class="two-column">

                    <div class="mini-card">

                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522202176988-66273c2fd55f?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="">

                        <div class="mini-title">
                            Simulation Prompting
                        </div>

                        <div class="mini-sub">
                            Train strategic thinking using role-based simulations.
                        </div>

                    </div>

                    <div class="mini-card">

                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1455390582262-044cdead277a?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="">

                        <div class="mini-title">
                            Critique Prompting
                        </div>

                        <div class="mini-sub">
                            Sharpen judgment through high-standard feedback loops.
                        </div>

                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

        <!-- CARD 5 -->

        <div class="card dark-card">

            <div class="content">

                <div class="small-tag">
                    Your Edge
                </div>

                <h2 style="color:white;">
                    Reflective Intelligence
                </h2>

                <p>
                    The people who benefit most from AI are not
                    necessarily the most technical.
                </p>

                <p>
                    They are the people who:
                </p>

                <ul style="margin-left:20px; line-height:2; color:#c5c5c5;">
                    <li>Ask layered questions</li>
                    <li>Notice subtle patterns</li>
                    <li>Refine thinking continuously</li>
                    <li>Iterate strategically</li>
                </ul>

            </div>

        </div>

        <!-- CARD 6 -->

        <div class="card">

            <div class="image-section">

                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1497366754035-f200968a6e72?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="">

            </div>

            <div class="content">

                <div class="small-tag">
                    Final Framework
                </div>

                <h2>
                    I.C.O.N.S
                </h2>

                <p>
                    Identity · Context · Outcome · Nuance · Structure
                </p>

                <div class="info-box">

                    <p>
                        Whenever you write a prompt,
                        mentally check these five dimensions.
                    </p>

                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        Designed for elegant thinking · Strategic cognition · Modern AI literacy
    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
